Where to buy fresh and inexpensive products (addresses) in Kiev this week

05 Nov 2019, 06:05

Agricultural fairs take place in the capital
Seasonal fairs will be held in Kiev this week to sell agricultural and processed products for all product groups. This was reported in the Department of Industry and Entrepreneurship Development of Kyiv City State Administration.
In particular, the fairs will continue:

November 5 (Tuesday):


in Holosiivskyi district - prosp. Nauky, 88, vul. Vladimirskaya, 80-86-A;
in Darnytskyi district - st. Yevhen Kharchenko, 41-47, prosp. Mykola Bazhan (footpath from Arcadia shopping mall to Osokorky metro station), intersection of Pavel Chubynsky and Yuri Paskhalin streets;
in Desnyanskiy district - st. Electrotechnical (from WOG - 2, 4-B, 6, 16, 10, 18, 26, 28, and from the other side - 5, 5-A, 7, 11, 9, 9-A to SHELL; Electrotechnical , 2-A, opposite the central entrance of the markets "Obriy-2000" and "Gloria-T");
